# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok ten people have been detained as suspects in a grenade attack that injured tajik president emomali rakhmonov , a russian news agency reported saturday .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (a / agency
            :mod (n / news)
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Russia")))
      :ARG1 (d / detain-01
            :ARG1 (p / person
                  :quant 10
                  :ARG2-of (s / suspect-01
                        :ARG1 (a2 / attack-01
                              :instrument (g / grenade)
                              :ARG0-of (ii / injure-01
                                    :ARG1 (p2 / person
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Emomali"
                                                :op2 "Rakhmonov")
                                          :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                                :ARG1 (c2 / country
                                                      :name (n4 / name
                                                            :op1 "Tajikistan"))
                                                :ARG2 (p3 / president)))))))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (s2 / saturday))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok makoto imaoka drove in the winning run in the eighth inning friday as the hanshin tigers rallied for an #-# win over the yomiuri giants in the central league 's season-opening game .
# ::alignments
(d / drive-02
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Makoto"
                  :op2 "Imaoka"))
      :ARG1 (r / run-02
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG0-of (w / win-01))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :time (r2 / rally-01
            :ARG1 (t / tiger
                  :mod (t2 / team
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Hanshin"
                              :op2 "Tigers")))
            :ARG2 (w2 / win-01
                  :ARG0 t
                  :ARG1 (t3 / team
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Yomiuri"
                              :op2 "Giant"))
                  :subevent-of (g / game
                        :ARG1-of (o / open-02
                              :ARG3 (l / league
                                    :mod (c / central))))))
      :time d2
      :day 8)

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok serbia 's prime minister warned saturday that giving independence to the u.n.-administered province of kosovo would create a regional problem .
# ::alignments
(w / warn-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Serbia"))
                  :ARG2 (m / minister
                        :mod (p2 / prime))))
      :ARG1 (c2 / create-01
            :ARG0 (g / give-01
                  :ARG1 (d / depend-01
                        :polarity -)
                  :ARG2 (p3 / province
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Kosovo")
                        :ARG1-of (a / administer-01
                              :ARG0 (o / organization
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "U.N.")))))
            :ARG1 (p4 / problem
                  :mod (r / region)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (s / saturday)))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Benjamin"
                                    :op2 "Netanyahu")

                                    :ARG2 (m / minister
                                          :topic (f / finance))))
                        :op3 (p5 / person
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Silvan"
                                    :op2 "Shalom")
                              :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG2 (m2 / minister
                                          :topic (f2 / foreign)))))))
      :ARG1 (p6 / person
            :name (n5 / name
                  :op1 "Ariel"
                  :op2 "Sharon")
            :ARG0-of (h4 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (m3 / minister
                        :mod (p7 / prime))))
      :ARG2 (c2 / chance-02
            :ARG0 p6
            :ARG1 (r / resume-01
                  :ARG0 p6
                  :ARG1 (t / talk-01
                        :ARG0 p6

                  :ARG0 p

                              :quant 1
                              :unit (d / day))
                        :ARG3 (d2 / die-01

                                    :mod (f2 / fellow)))
                        :location (j / jail)))))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok in the surprise hit show of ireland 's month-long festival celebrating samuel beckett , who was born on april ## one hundred years ago , the star actor does not say a word : michael gambon sits on a bed and listens to a disembodied recorded woman 's voice for about ## minutes .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :polarity -
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (a / act-01
                  :mod (s2 / star)))
      :ARG1 (w / word-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (s3 / sit-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Michael"
                                    :op2 "G gambon"))
                        :ARG2 (b / bed))
                  :op2 (l / listen-01
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (v / voice
                              :poss (w2 / woman
                                    :ARG1-of (r / record-01)
                                    :ARG1-of (d / disembodied-01)))
                        :duration (a3 / about
                              :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                                    :quant 1
                                    :unit (m / minute))))))
      :time (s4 / show-04
            :ARG1 (f / festival
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Samuel"
                        :op2 "Beckett")
                  :ARG1-of (b2 / bear-02
                        :time (b3 / before
                              :op1 (n3 / now)
                              :quant t
                              :quant 100
                              :unit (y / year))))
            :poss (c / country
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Ireland"))
            :ARG0-of (c2 / celebrate-01
                  :ARG1 p2))
      :ARG1-of (h / hit-02)
      :ARG0-of (s5 / surprise-01))

# ::id 8 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the european commission on tuesday predicted that the eu and eurozone will grow in #### at a modest rate of #.# percent as the economy moves from a sharp recession to a hesitant and fragile recovery .
# ::alignments
(p / predict-01
      :ARG0 (c / commission
            :mod (o / organization
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "European"
                        :op2 "Union")))
      :ARG1 (g / grow-01
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 o
                  :op2 o)
            :manner (r / rate-entity-91
                  :ARG1 (p2 / percentage-entity
                        :value 1)
                  :ARG2 (m / modest))
            :time (m2 / move-01
                  :ARG1 (e / economy)
                  :ARG2 (r2 / recover-01
                        :ARG1 e
                        :ARG2 (r3 / recession-02
                              :ARG1-of (s / sharp-02))
                        :ARG3 r2
                        :ARG1 e
                        :mod (f / fragile)
                        :ARG0-of (h / hesitate-01))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

# ::id 14 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Dale"
                                          :op2 "Pearson")

                                    :mod (m2 / mystery))
                              :ARG1 n
                              :mod s2))
                  :mod (t2 / too)))
      :snt3 (p4 / purveyor
            :ARG0-of (s4 / sing-01
                  :ARG1 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (m3 / murder-01)
                        :op2 (m4 / mayhem)))
            :domain (p5 / person

                        :mod (t2 / technology))))

                        :op1 "Europe")))

            :ARG1 m)

      :degree (w / well))
